//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Bridge Rectifier

    ##########################
    Schematics    
    
    #              A  B  C
    #              ~  ~  ~        
    #              o  o  o
    #              |  |  |           
    #              |  |  |              
    #  +------>|---o--|--|---->|--------+
    #  |              |  |              |
    #  |------>|------o--|---->|--------|
    #  |                 |              |
    #  |------>|---------o---->|--------|
    #  |                                |
    #  |                                |
    #  o (-)                            o (+)
    
    
    ##########################
    Test without power
    
    Set DMM to diode test
    Every diode should have values of about 0.48 ( - to A, A to +, etc)
    All diodes should be at 0.85 ( - to + )
    Opposite direction of every diode should be OL

    ##########################
    Test with power
    
    Since A, B and C are from 3 phase incoming AC supply, test phase to phase voltage
    (-) and (+) are DC output, so test DC voltage, should be about 580VDC (530VDC to 590VDC)

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
[End]


















